text: @BBCNewsnight @katierazz @sallyches I had symptoms prior to high temperature for about 10 days. NHS 111 indicated every day that I did not have symptoms of COVID19. I think they got the symptomology wrong and this has led to 10s of thousands catching and dying from the virus.
